Package: embeddingtools
Title: A Package for Annotating Text Data With Pre-Trained Word Embedding Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Damien", "Crone", email = "damien.crone@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package for annotating text data with pre-trained word embedding models. Contains basic functions for tasks such as (1) loading pre-trained models, (2) computing vector representations of concepts comprising terms in a model's vocabulary, (3) computing vector representations of texts, (4) computing the similarity between texts and concepts.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), text2vec
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
